Package: standardize
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Standardizing Model Frames
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Christopher D.", "Eager",
    email = "eagerstats@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: standardize provides tools which allow all of the regression
    predictors in a model frame to be placed on the same (or similar) scales.
